headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid FDX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 27.9% since April 2025, FedEx (currently trading at $237.60 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 15.1%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
